formulas.</definition> 	<topic>structured documents and XML</topic> </entry><entry>	<sort>metadata</sort> 	<term>metadata</term> 	<definition>Literally "data about data," a set of data that describes and gives information about other data.</definition> 	<topic>structured documents and XML</topic> </entry><entry>	<sort>ontologies</sort> 	<term>ontologies</term> 	<definition>A vocabulary of terms whose meaning is formally defined.</definition> 	<topic>structured documents and XML</topic> </entry><entry>	<sort>rdf (Resource Definition Framework)</sort> 	<term>RDF (Resource Definition Framework)</term> 	<definition>A framework for describing and interchanging metadata.</definition> 	<topic>structured documents and XML</topic> </entry><entry>	<sort>really simple syndication (rss)</sort> 	<term>Really Simple Syndication (RSS)</term> 	<definition>An XML format for distributing news headlines on the Web.</definition> 	<topic>structured documents and XML</topic> </entry><entry>	<sort>structured document</sort> 	<term>structured document</term> 	<definition>A document whose structure conforms to a certain set of rules.</definition> 	<topic>structured documents and XML</topic> </entry><entry>	<sort>uniform resource locator (URL)</sort> 	<term>Uniform Resource Locator (URL)</term> 	<definition>A scheme for referencing the specific location of a resource.</definition> 	<topic>structured documents and XML</topic> </entry><entry>	<sort>xhtml</sort> 	<term>XHTML</term> 	<definition>Just like HTML, but based on XML rules to support integration of different data in the same document.</definition> 	<topic>structured documents and XML</topic> </entry><entry>	<sort>xml</sort> 	<term>XML (eXtensible Markup Language)</term> 	<definition>A standard for exchanging structured data.</definition> 	<topic>structured documents and XML</topic> </entry><entry>	<sort>xslt</sort>	<term>XSLT (eXtensible Stylesheet Language Transformations)</term>	<definition>Language for converting one XML document into another.</definition>	<topic>structured documents and XML</topic></entry></glossary>